#. metadata.json->name
msgid "Mini-Calc Applet"
msgstr "Mini-Calc Applet"

#. metadata.json->description
msgid ""
"Very simple and minimalistic but yet powerful calculator that evaluates "
"JavaScript expressions."
msgstr "非常簡潔、極簡風格但功能強大的計算機，可執行 JavaScript 運算式。"

#. settings-schema.json->panel-options->title
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "設定"

#. settings-schema.json->keyboard-section->title
msgid "Keyboard"
msgstr "鍵盤"

#. settings-schema.json->input-section->title
msgid "Number Format"
msgstr "數字格式"

#. settings-schema.json->history-section->title
msgid "Expression and Result History"
msgstr "運算式與計算結果記錄"

#. settings-schema.json->keyToggle->description
msgid "Show / hide mini calculator"
msgstr "顯示／隱藏小計算機"

#. settings-schema.json->convertLocaleNumberSeparators->description
msgid "Convert numbers in current locale's format to JS numbers"
msgstr "將目前語系格式的數字轉換為 JS 數字格式"

#. settings-schema.json->convertLocaleNumberSeparatorsHelp->description
msgid ""
"e.g. for the German locale convert `1,2 + 3,4` to `1.2 + 3.4`. Makes pasting "
"number easier."
msgstr ""
"例如：在德語語系中，將 `1,2 + 3,4` 轉換為 `1.2 + 3.4`，讓貼上數字更方便。"

#. settings-schema.json->recentHistoryMaxLength->description
msgid "Max number of recent expressions"
msgstr "最近運算式的最大數量"

#. settings-schema.json->historyMaxDisplayLength->description
msgid "Max length of expression history"
msgstr "運算式記錄的最大長度"
